Description: 
    Bookmarks manager with tabs using tmux.

Usage: xl-mark <Option>

Option: One of the following:

    -h , --help:
        Print this help page.

    -a , --add:
        Add a new bookmark.

    -g , --get:
        Open bookmarks menu.

    -l , --list:
        List bookmarks from a single category.

Configuration:
    - Files in ~/.config/xlotus/bookmarks are categories for bookmarks.
    - Filename is the category name that lists bookmarks within using fzf.
    - You must have a single file named default in ~/.config/xlotus/bookmarks .
